OL,3,CFive rural nurseries saved from
OL,4,Cclosure following U-turn
OL,6,FParents from the Borders have been
OL,7,Fthanked for their "invaluable support"
OL,8,Fafter plans to temporarily close five
OL,9,Frural nurseries have been scrapped.
OL,11,FEarlier this year, the Scottish
OL,12,FBorders Council (SBC) drafted plans to
OL,13,Fmothball schools in Cockburnspath,
OL,14,FEdnam, Oxton, Yetholm and Walkerburn
OL,15,Ffor the next academic year.
OL,17,FBut amid the public backlash, members
OL,18,Fof full council agreed to "set aside"
OL,19,Fthat decision on May 9, reports the
OL,20,FLocal Democracy Reporting Service.
