OL,3,CFive rural nurseries saved from
OL,4,Cclosure following U-turn
OL,6,FAfter approving a motion to keep all
OL,7,Fthe nurseries open for the next
OL,8,Facademic year, the local authority has
OL,9,Fnow come up with individualised plans
OL,10,Ffor all nurseries following
OL,11,Fconsultations with parents and carers,
OL,12,Fin place for August 2025.
OL,14,FCouncillors agreed on the new setup
OL,15,Fduring an Executive Committee meeting
OL,16,Fon 6 June 2025. Members also endorsed
OL,17,Fplans to establish an Early Years
OL,18,Fpolicy for 2026/27, with a report to
OL,19,Fbe brought to full council in October.
