OL,6,FCouncillor Julie Pirone, SBC's
OL,7,Fexecutive member for Education, Youth
OL,8,FDevelopment and Lifelong Learning,
OL,9,Fsays the new education plan "addresses
OL,10,Fmany concerns" raised.
OL,12,FShe said: "We can now move forward
OL,13,Fwith the implementation of the
OL,14,Fapproved models, which include co-
OL,15,Flocation of nursery and primary
OL,16,Fchildren, as well as the retention of
OL,17,FWalkerburn Nursery after relooking at
OL,18,Fnumbers of local children including
OL,19,Ftwo-year-olds.
